					]
				},
				"description": "**Add_Book** : This is **POST** type API request used for adding the new books into to the Library.\n\n**Base URI:** [https://rahulshettyacademy.com](https://rahulshettyacademy.com)\n\n**Parameters:** /Library/Addbook.php[](http://216.10.245.166)\n\n<u><b>Note</b></u><u>-</u> _aisle value should be number only. Isbn should be unique to insert. So provide random isbn which makes unique._"
			},
